positions.title: Wipro Limited
positions.description:
Working as Full Stack Developer in an agile project with Java as the major application language. Role is to deal with customers, gather requirements, design analysis with team, developing the solutions for the functionalities, support to quality assurance teams, analyzing and solving the defects and to deploy the code bases in different environments.

Client is a major satellite television provider at US and is one among the top 200 Fortune companies. The project is based on the Work Force Management (WFM) of the Client's resources for fulfilling the In-home services work orders.
